


  // Products Management ( PM )
  -------------------------------
  
  
  uri:  /products
  -----------------
  
  GET  : /products      --> render all products
  GET  : /products/id   --> render product
  
  POST : /products      --> create new product
  
  PUT  : /products/id   --> create/update product
  
  DELETE : /products/id --> delete product
  
